Hollywood’s glitterati shouldn’t have been surprised at finding themselves the butt of jokes by Ricky Gervais at this year’s Golden Globe Awards. He’s foul-mouthed and he goes for the jugular, skewering vanities left, right and centre. Many were the nervous laughs when Gervais advised the stars that if they were called up on stage to receive an award, they should not “use it as a platform to make a political speech”. “You are in no position to lecture the public about anything. You know nothing about the real world. Most of you spent less time in school than Greta Thunberg....